{"type": "article", "id": 8313, "title": "Osiloi 梳妆台", "description": "", "date": "2015-04-10T07:19:06Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 4, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234726dYE4XvbNLrOj6AhC.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t设计师 Rui Pereira 和 Ryosuke Fukusada 共同设计了一个梳妆台系列，包括一个梳妆台，梳妆凳，托盒，毛巾架，竹镜，三角竹架，灯以及竹杯。这个系列设计的核心是座敷团，也就是图中这个矮凳子。降低座位的高度使人们获得了新的空间体验，整体配色柔和温暖，为化妆营造放松的气氛，材质上使用了 COTTO 陶瓷和天然的竹具，看起来兼备自然和现代化。这套作品将会参与 2015 米兰设计周，参加 COTTO 陶瓷主办的 “Perspective 3-space of Beauty” 现场活动。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052347222BErYJ5Gl9ezH17j.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.73349633\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052347233WDqoZ142wYBnQt9.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.72371638\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234723ujcdDI0Toir7n6UY.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.73349633\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234723r2ubyPJN4TM3USY0.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.73349633\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234724zc6bdESjCrBNHOav.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.72860636\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234724ajwVlT4gd9oYWeZ8.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.73349633\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234725vWDS7NaAB3jO4cGb